<% content_for :title, "About Us - Requiems API" %>

<div class="min-h-screen bg-gray-50 py-16">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 md:p-12">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">About Requiems API</h1>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8">
          Building production-ready APIs for developers worldwide.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-600 p-4 mb-8">
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Requiems API is a product by <a href="https://bobadilla.tech" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 font-semibold">Bobadilla Technologies</a>, a team dedicated to building developer-first tools and infrastructure.
          </p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          Requiems API provides developers with enterprise-grade API infrastructure without the enterprise complexity.
          We believe in making powerful APIs accessible to developers of all sizes, from indie hackers to large enterprises.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">What We Offer</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-6">
          <li>Email validation and verification APIs</li>
          <li>Text utility APIs (Lorem Ipsum, advice, quotes, random words)</li>
          <li>Enterprise-grade infrastructure hosted in the EU</li>
          <li>Transparent pricing with no hidden fees</li>
          <li>Developer-first documentation and support</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Our Values</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Developer Experience</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              We obsess over making our APIs easy to integrate and delightful to use.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Reliability</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              99.99% uptime SLA backed by enterprise infrastructure and monitoring.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Transparency</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              Clear pricing, detailed documentation, and honest communication.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Privacy</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              EU-hosted infrastructure with GDPR compliance built-in from day one.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          Have questions or want to learn more?
          <%= link_to "Get in touch", contact_path, class: "text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 font-medium" %>
          or email us at
          <a href="mailto:eliaz@bobadilla.tech" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 font-medium">eliaz@bobadilla.tech</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
